Lapsr — Changelog
==================


v1.0.3 (latest)
--------------------
- Fixed scrollbar positioning in lap list


v1.0.2
------
- Fixed lap table column alignment
- Fixed scrollbar overlapping +Delta column
- Sticky header now inside scroll container


v1.0.1
------
- Replaced innerHTML with DOM API in lap list renderer
  for improved security


v1.0.0
------
- Initial release
- Start, pause, and reset
- Lap tracking with delta times
- Best and worst lap highlighted automatically
- Timer runs in background while popup is closed
- No storage, no network requests, no external dependencies
- Fonts bundled locally (Share Tech Mono, Rajdhani)